OL,3,CTeachers and some NHS staff set for
OL,4,C5.5% pay rise
OL,6,FRachel Reeves is expected to approve
OL,7,Fabove-inflation pay rises for millions
OL,8,Fof public sector workers next week.
OL,10,FIt would mean teachers and around 1.3
OL,11,Fmillion NHS staff could be in line for
OL,12,Fa 5.5% pay increase.
OL,14,FThe Chancellor is set to respond to
OL,15,Fthe recommendations of independent pay
OL,16,Freview bodies on Monday.
OL,18,FThe pay rise would cost an extra #3.5
OL,19,Fbillion, but the government could face
OL,20,Ffurther industrial action if the
OL,21,Fincrease is refused.
