OL,6,FMs Reeves will also argue in
OL,7,FParliament that the Tories left Labour
OL,8,Fwith a dire spending inheritance,
OL,9,Fincluding a #20 billion black hole.
OL,11,FShe could reportedly also announce
OL,12,Fdelays to a string of major capital
OL,13,Fprojects to plug the shortfall.
OL,15,FSir Keir Starmer has previously
OL,16,Facknowledged there would be a cost if
OL,17,Ffailing to follow the recommendations
OL,18,Fof the pay review bodies led to a
OL,19,Ffresh wave of industrial disputes in
OL,20,Fthe public services.
