OL,4,C5.5% pay rise
OL,6,FLabour did not deny reports that Ms
OL,7,FReeves could on Monday make the same
OL,8,Fargument as she signs off on the pay
OL,9,Fincreases despite the shortfall in
OL,10,Fgovernment funding plans.
OL,12,FThe findings of a Treasury spending
OL,13,Faudit she will detail will reveal "the
OL,14,Ftrue scale of the damage the
OL,15,FConservatives have done to the public
OL,16,Ffinances", a Labour source said.
OL,18,FAn early assessment has reportedly
OL,19,Ffound a nearly #20 billion annual gap
OL,20,Fbetween revenues and funding
OL,21,Fcommitments.
